occurrenceRemarks: Only previous collection seen Blanchet 2828 (Type). Shrub to 3 m. Leaves strongly coriaceous, dark glossy green above, paler beneath. Cuter tepals yellow green, inner yellowish with deep crimson base. Anthers crinson stigmas pale. Fruit grey-green.
